    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Route new orders with Shopify and MySQL without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Order Fulfillment · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nRoute new orders with Shopify and MySQL without manual work. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual fulfillment is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nOn Shopify Event → Pull Side A (MySQL) → Diff the Two Systems → Create Missing in Google Sheets → Gather Sync Results → Guard Non-Empty email → Tag Pipeline Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to order fulfillment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating fulfillment in e-commerce\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; MySQL connection; Shopify access token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "6388ebf7-9a0c-b70d-6dc2-748346b7f33e",
